If you'd like to learn more about the thinking system in your brain,

00:04:20.833 --> 00:04:22.793
Check out the book "Thinking Fast and Slow"

00:04:22.941 --> 00:04:23.767
by Daniel Kahneman

00:04:23.913 --> 00:04:25.809
Which covers it in great detail

